{"tid":2290471,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"PTU涉偷信用卡購物 准保釋下月再訊","createTime":"2020-11-18T04:33:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-18T08:06:41.000Z","uid":184679,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6dff8f9d2ca2cd8fdb01fe25175fa0084fdd0363","tid":2290471,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T04:33:52.000Z","msg":"28歲駐守港島區的機動部隊警員，涉嫌於去年10月偷取他人信用卡購物，被控一項盜竊罪及兩項以欺騙手段取得財產罪，今在東區裁判法院提堂。案件將押後至12月16日提再訊，以索取法律意見。被告獲准以1000港元保釋，期間不得離開香港，須居於報稱地址。<br />\n<br />\n被告李卓軒被控於2019年10月14日，在太古城中心5樓的MOViE MOViE Cityplaza 偷竊一張信用卡，並在未授權下用此信用卡在該地消費33港元。後同日又於銅鑼灣希慎廣場的Apple Store用同一張信用卡消費約2萬5港元。警員被控一項盜竊罪及兩項以欺騙手段取得財產罪。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/ptu涉盜信用卡購物-准保釋下月再訊-033300892.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2Fptu%E6%B6%89%E7%9B%9C%E4%BF%A1%E7%94%A8%E5%8D%A1%E8%B3%BC%E7%89%A9-%E5%87%86%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B%E4%B8%8B%E6%9C%88%E5%86%8D%E8%A8%8A-033300892.html&d=KoeRi8LHiva86SpHjnbz1e2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=6583cf1f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/ptu涉盜信用卡購物-准保釋下月再訊-033300892.html</a>"},{"pid":"dcf3b0ff4dff91cc5fe5175469476c0c19622bd5","tid":2290471,"uid":98172,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T04:39:01.000Z","msg":"PTU= Police Thief Unit<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b15c1b6aa7696b8f4b6f4c9d05ea42322368c774","tid":2290471,"uid":334720,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"dcf3b0ff4dff91cc5fe5175469476c0c19622bd5","tid":2290471,"uid":98172,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T04:39:01.000Z","msg":"PTU= Police Thief Unit<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T04:50:41.000Z","msg":"Professional Thief Unit"},{"pid":"2b32d3ac6cec253cd630d3f77e683b0f82805073","tid":2290471,"uid":3241,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T05:01:35.000Z","msg":"人渣敗類集中地<br />\n真係